## SSH / SFTP Access

For SSH-based deployment or file synchronization:

```bash
# Set up SSH client with key-based auth
task ssh:setup -- --remote-host prod.example.com --remote-user deploy

# Validate connectivity
task ssh:validate -- --remote-host prod.example.com
```

See [SSH_SFTP.md](SSH_SFTP.md) for server hardening, SFTP-only users,
and VS Code SFTP extension setup.
